        <Parent_String>sodium chloride by form [300386507], sodium chloride [300183888], sodium compounds [300210797], sodium and sodium compounds [300419469], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
